

/1/to start the system, enter the WorkSpace

cd ~/catkin_ws

/2/next, setup

source devel/setup.bash

/3/enter main work folder

cd ~/catkin_ws/src/my_dynamixel_tutorial

/4/launch controller

roslaunch my_dynamixel_tutorial controller_manager.launch

/5/this makes the terminal unusable, so make a new terminal, start from step 1 and skip step 4 and 5

/6/launch desired system

//a/ roslaunch my_dynamixel_tutorial start_tilt_controller.launch
[INOPERABLE]//b/ roslaunch my_dynamixel_tutorial start_dual_motor_controller.launch [WOULD GET STUCK WAITING FROM RESPONSE FROM MANAGER]
//c/ roslaunch my_dynamixel_tutorial start_meta_controller.launch

/7/control the desired system (if applicable)

//a/ rostopic pub -1 /tilt_controller/command std_msgs/Float64 -- <radian value, from -2.617 to +2.617, no sideways arrows needed just straight number>
[INOPERABLE]//b/ rostopic pub -1 /dual_motor_controller/command std_msgs/Float64 -- <radian value, //a/>
//c/ rostopic pub -1 /jointXX_controller/command std_msgs/Float64 -- <radian value, see //a/>
